<A>__{tatiana kisses paul.}
<C>__{colonel oliver }
<D>__{zamacanga ghana. a plane will land at the airport tomorrow and the named families will be flown to kenya. two un trucks will be here at 7 a.m. the named families must be ready to leave then. voice calls out.}
<C>__{tutsi woman}
<D>__{colonel, sir. why not take us all to the airport? we can wait there to obtain visas.}
<C>__{colonel oliver}
<D>__{i can't do that. our camp at the airport is overwhelmed already. we could not defend you there. you are better to stay here and work to get an exit visa.}
<A>__{oliver jumps from the stage, pushes through the crowd. paul's pov: odette and jean baptiste are silently devastated. he pushes through to the colonel now surrounded by those who didn't make the list.}
